    <item>
      <title>乐高 CEO 希望通过更多游戏交易复制《堡垒之夜》的成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐高首席执行官表示，乐高公司与 Epic Games 合作推出的《堡垒之夜》大获成功，自推出以来已覆盖 8300 万人，该公司目前正在寻求新的数字合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/lego-ceo-wants-to-copy-fortnite-success-with-more-game-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆克什·安巴尼预计将在年度股东大会上提供有关 Reliance Jio 和零售业 IPO 的详细信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当亚洲首富穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 于周四发表备受期待的年度公开演讲时，信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 的股东们将会仔细分析他的讲话，以了解其电信和零售巨头上市的具体细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/ambani-s-reliance-agm-may-offer-clues-on-reliance-jio-reliance-retail-ipos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 04:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国空军将用瑞典战斗机取代老式 F-16</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thai-air-force-to-replace-old-f-16s-with-swedish-fighter-jets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据泰国皇家空军周二发表的声明称，泰国皇家空军将购买一定数量的瑞典鹰狮战斗机，以取代老化的美国制造的 F-16 战机队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/thai-air-force-to-replace-old-f-16s-with-swedish-fighter-jets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果因业务重点转变削减在线服务部门职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/apple-cuts-about-100-services-jobs-as-part-of-priority-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司采取罕见举措，在其数字服务部门裁员约 100 人，这是该关键部门工作重点转变的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/apple-cuts-about-100-services-jobs-as-part-of-priority-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利三菱日联金融集团和花旗集团上调目标价 乐天股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/rakuten-surges-as-morgan-stanley-mufg-citi-raise-price-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利三菱日联证券等券商因乐天集团移动业务的成功而上调其目标价，此后，乐天集团股价攀升至 2022 年 4 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/rakuten-surges-as-morgan-stanley-mufg-citi-raise-price-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
